The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Tuesday, July 13, 2004 				 Riots rap
																								New Delhi, July 12: The Supreme Court today issued a notice to the Gujarat government following an application alleging that the state government had suppressed facts regarding grant of bail to several riot accused, reports our legal correspondent.																								A three-judge bench of Justices Ruma Pal, S.B. Sinha and S.H. Kapadia directed the state government to file a reply in two weeks. 
